do you manage to read any science fiction or any other fiction in between all
your writing joints? I read some science fiction and I try to keep up with

08:30.420 --> 08:44.200
science fiction. I try to it's impossible to read all the science fiction that
is being put out. I think you would get total vision if you did. you'd get a

08:44.200 --> 09:03.740
good many confusing signals if you did. I read a lot for information. I am a
history buff with emphasis on the Civil War and the settlement of our country

09:03.740 --> 09:14.840
and I have a few favorite authors. Steinbeck, Hemingway, Thomas Lewis.

09:17.460 --> 09:22.260
